me":"2019-07-25T10:10:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《緊急》堅持人強馬壯 新加聯署齊推<br />\n麻煩大家推呢2個post上熱門同時將消息散開各處</span></strong><br />\n🥳7.26 香港國際機場集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n🥳7.28 母忘上環 - 追究上環開槍責任<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n🎆香港🎆時代革命🎆爭取五大訴求🎆<br />\n📢1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n📢2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性&nbsp;<br />\n📢3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究&nbsp;<br />\n📢4. 全面實行雙普選&nbsp;<br />\n📢5. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">睇到最底 內容包括：「運動時間」 「聯署」 《會加入新聯署 記得去簽》 白宮需要係電郵內確認先叫完成 就得係電郵㩒連結 唔好懶 所有活動必須同時進行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[721]有手足頭部中槍危殆 吐血不止<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355224</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大穫到咁無外國人知? 我要將７２１上環最恐怖１分鐘半片段流出到國際 !!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n蘋果A2: 7.21遊行後爆衝突　 千警上環亂彈清場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1. 有義士腳部中槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157863977222448%3Fs%3D1279554103%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=4af6953c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 有記者直接被催淚彈打中<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcTeVHAuMLP4%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=78c6c011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a><br />\n<br />\n西上環事件整合 求更多新聞同義士消息 推上去 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357053</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家幫手<br />\n1. 了解並更新上述受傷人士最新狀況<br />\n2. 找出更多未知義士受傷的資訊及片段<br />\n3. 廣傳讓更多人關注上環事發經過及受傷<br />\n<br />\n☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻<br />\n持續不合作運動「兄弟爬山，各自努力」<br />\n- 18區連儂場<br />\n- 沙田新城市廣場<br />\n<br />\n🥳7.26 香港國際機場集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcyoE62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcyoE62.png&h=3d22b6f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🥳7.27 元朗反恐襲 - 踢走鄉黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355504</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n😎建議遊行提早於😎上午十時至中午十二時期間開始😎以確保安全😎男女老幼齊反恐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Css8RdS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCss8RdS.jpg&h=c9e2fd1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🥳7.28 母忘上環 - 追究上環開槍責任<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUbxysn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUbxysn.jpg&h=d3d247fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🥳8.4 將軍澳反送中大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356143</a> <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n🥳8.4 港島西大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356505</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7k2VJF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7k2VJF.png&h=b71dcf11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請各位努力推po以提出遊行時間修訂<br />\n已取消或延期:<br />\n<br />\n兩條戰線同樣重要 但係請各位心水清&nbsp;<br />\n任何一方都不能忽視 以防誤中港共圈套<br />\n亦避免被各方妖孽分散注意力 必須將火力對準政權<br />\n政府務必回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n簽咗都要🙏廣傳🙏快夠數💪唔好話冇用就唔做，唔理效果有咩都必撐，團結是力量💪<br />\n<br />\n🖕🖕🖕見指中聯辦😡😡勾結香港黑社會😡😡策劃元朗恐怖襲擊聯署🖕🖕🖕<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frestore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=f84fbad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0</a><br />\n<br />\n🧐🧐【元朗黑夜連登獨立調查委員會】🧐🧐<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F34AmN69rRScNafEC9&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=3d454f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9</a><br />\n<br />\n🤬🤬要求馬會撤銷何君堯會藉🤬🤬<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg/viewform?fbclid=IwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3xwKFgJRHHW4pIB7RjQoJNfoJSBFyWzDDzY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg%2Fviewform%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3xwKFgJRHHW4pIB7RjQoJNfoJSBFyWzDDzY4&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=507808b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg/viewform?fbclid=IwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3xwKFgJRHHW4pIB7RjQoJNfoJSBFyWzDDzY4</a><br />\n<br />\n😡😡投訴李漢民有違法公職人員行為失當😡😡<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\nEmail : csbcomp@csb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n🙏🙏所有香港大學學生、舊生以及職員參與聯署，要求香港大學校長張翔履行社會使命。🙏🙏<a href=\"https://forms.gle/UAVikwsyCmdDEyy76\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FUAVikwsyCmdDEyy76&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=d9da5357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/UAVikwsyCmdDEyy76</a><br />\n<br />\n🤭我唔捨得何君堯去美國🤭<br />\n🥳大家快聯署留底佢全家🥳<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 21, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas?fbclid=IwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fmake-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=1dfdb371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas?fbclid=IwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M</a><br />\n<br />\n🥰🤩[遍地攬炒] 一人一信幫何君堯律師世世代代享受大灣區榮耀🥰🤩😁內含教學😁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351572</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 21, 2019：人道支援聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6YZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=925ec24d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens</a><br />\n<br />\n😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡😡<br />\n銀行商店拉閘「靜過十號波」<br />\n指揮官拍膊與黑幫論形勢<br />\n大狀：必須獨立調查<br />\n警遲到場：睇唔到錶<br />\n999無人聽 市民向消防求救<br />\n「飛天南」蘇醒 稱被打無傷痕<br />\n林鄭重國徽輕視港人安危<br />\n記者叫特首「講返句人話」<br />\n王志民自誇中聯辦巍然不動<br />\n建制派反指示威者「挑機」<br />\n總商會轉軚促撤法：失職官員須問責<br />\n何君堯飯局 惡煞食飽打人<br />\n百人毀議辦 轟何勾結黑幫<br />\n被指撬閘 元朗區會副主席辯稱勸交<br />\n賴上環清場 盧偉聰：調配人手需時<br />\n元朗黑夜 還原白色恐襲8小時<br />\n休班紀律部隊自發趕到救人<br />\n搵仔媽媽︰警無資格𢭃人工<br />\n少年痛哭元朗沉淪<br />\n眾志成員遇襲傷頭<br />\n林卓廷轟建制無恥<br />\n青年護花慘遭狂鞭<br />\n柳俊江義載變血人<br />\n居民攜衫救人被毆<br />\n三區讓路 7.27「光復元朗」<br />\n巿民港鐵內受傷可索償<br />\n遇襲記者︰好似屍殺列車<br />\n不滿警黑合作 民政局職員疑罷工<br />\n國際將香港新疆相提並論<br />\n台灣不再信一國兩制謊言<br />\n警再開槍射頭 示威者重創<br />\n記者遭速龍舉槍棍指嚇<br />\n濃煙下槍聲四起 示威者變活靶<br />\n警不作為 黑幫肆虐元、屯、荃 變死城"},{"pid":"00dd544fd385f547bdc0ed6d6b7b64bf1b0b6038","tid":1364172,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bc8afd8d4595cfcb21e96873f1b36565f3a21ef1","tid":1364172,"uid":231691,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"25d011fe3b26557b3289fdd17dc22a2735c738ae","tid":1364172,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"Cafe de carol (yuen long)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除咗每個禮拜嘅遊行 都想食好西休息下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:11:20.000Z","msg":"咩意思，cafe de carol 唔係好西呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863fdbae559108c8a2d119687a174d62f235fcde","tid":1364172,"uid":192766,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4034212b63c6f04b87dabf64a5bc8150c6ecaca","tid":1364172,"uid":156466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:30:29.000Z","msg":"我有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":